Value IP_ADDRESS (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value TYPE (Static|Dynamic)
Value MAC_ADDRESS ([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}(?::[0-9A-Fa-f]{2}){5})
Value VENDOR (.+?)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value TIMEOUT (.+?)

Start
  ^${IP_ADDRESS}\s+${TYPE}\s+${MAC_ADDRESS}\s+${VENDOR}\s{2,}${INTERFACE}\s+${TIMEOUT}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^.*$$
